item.description:
MT - TW
The plain truth is hard to accept: the number of high IQ nodes (individuals) in a nation &amp; the degree of connectivity between them (density of the graph edges) decide the line between its victory and defeat. &hellip;
Power differential between the pa~nchanetra &amp; rest is quite a bit in terms of most of the basics: energy, nukes, militech, high IQ individuals working towards a common goal.
